  "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon|Au Gratin Potatoes": "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon: this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat meets this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon|Bone Marrow": "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon: this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. Whiskey depth meets the starter's fat and umami — both land heavy. A headliner opener.",
  "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon|Bone-In Filet": "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon: this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Whiskey depth, oak, and sweetness carry beef weight — the drink scrubs fat and echoes char. A headliner steakhouse cocktail.",
