  "Aged Super-Premium Bourbon|Mushrooms": "Aged super-premium bourbon alongside the mushrooms — the earthy mushroom butter reads against the bourbon's leather and tobacco notes. Age softens proof; the mushroom's umami gets the spotlight. One of the cleanest luxury-pour pairings on the card.",
