  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Maker's Mark": "Au Gratin Potatoes: cheese and cream meet Maker's 90-proof softness. Cleanly matched; solid without standing out.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Maker's Mark Cellar Aged": "Au Gratin Potatoes: cheese and cream richness meet Maker's Mark Cellar Aged's mature caramel. Strong; same register.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Muga Reserva": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Never Say Die Small Batch": "Au Gratin Potatoes: cheese-and-cream meets Yorkshire-aged bourbon. Strong; novel maturation gives the side a unique voice.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Nickel & Nickel Cabernet": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Odette Cabernet Sauvignon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Old Fitzgerald 7 Year": "Au Gratin Potatoes: cheese-and-cream meets 100-proof wheated. Strong; bonded wheat honey sits with richness cleanly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Old Fitzgerald 9 Year": "Au Gratin Potatoes: cheese-and-cream meets aged wheated BIB. Strong; mature honey and oak sit with richness at full register.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Opus One": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Paloma": "Reposado tequila, vanilla syrup, fresh grapefruit. The grapefruit's bitterness and the reposado's citrus profile fight our manchego gratin's savory cream. Paloma belongs with chicken, salmon, or lighter seafood — not potato sides.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Peju Cabernet Sauvignon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
