  "Brussels and Belly|Bone Marrow": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. Shared-opener territory — starter and supporting plate run alongside each other. Strong — cohesive opener.",
