  "Brussels and Belly|Bowdie's Old Fashioned": "Buffalo Trace muddled with our rum-soaked cherries, orange, and Angostura over a large cube. The bourbon's caramel and our lardons' brown sugar align perfectly; the cherry-rum sweetness matches the pork-belly's sweet crust.",
