  "Burrata|Spiced / Flavored Rum": "Burrata: the burrata's creamy, fresh dairy mildness meets this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth. Aged spirit's oak and vanilla against a starter — depth meets the opening course. Works as a pour-alongside.",
