  "Burrata|The Tomahawk": "Burrata: the burrata's creamy, fresh dairy mildness meets this marbled ribeye's fatty richness, smoky crust, and bold beef expression. Starter-into-steak flow — the opener sets up the main without stealing from it. Avoid — the starter overshadows or clashes with the main.",
