  "Burrata|White / Light Rum": "Burrata: the burrata's creamy, fresh dairy mildness meets this white rum's clean sugarcane, tropical lift, and light frame. The spirit functions as a palate-setter here rather than a true counterpart to the plate. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
