  "Cream Liqueur|Creme Brulee": "Cream liqueur and creme brulee — textures mirror, flavors layer. Baileys' whiskey-vanilla or Buffalo Trace Cream's bourbon-forward profile both pick up the custard's egg-and-cream richness while the caramelized sugar crust gives the pairing its backbone. A clean, commercially-reliable dessert pair.",
