  "Cream Liqueur|The Tomahawk": "Cream Liqueur: this sweet cream liqueur's dessert-adjacent lushness meets this marbled ribeye's fatty richness, smoky crust, and bold beef expression. Sweet or herbal liqueur against a savory plate — register mismatch. Avoid — not a mid-plate pour.",
  "Creamed Spinach|1792 Small Batch": "Creamed Spinach: dairy richness meets Barton small-batch. Strong; spicy-sweet sits with richness at balanced register.",
  "Creamed Spinach|1792 Sweet Wheat": "Creamed Spinach: dairy richness meets sweet-wheat. Strong; distinctive wheat-sweetness sits with cream cleanly.",
  "Creamed Spinach|1881 Napa Valley": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. A bright-meets-rich headliner.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Aged Super-Premium Bourbon": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Alexander Valley Cyrus": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Alexander Valley Homestead Red": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Works — clean if not dominant.",
  "Creamed Spinach|American Single Malt / Tennessee": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this American single malt's charcoal-filtered vanilla, caramel, and medium frame. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — aligned weight.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Approachable Rye": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this approachable rye's pepper-and-herbal spice on a medium frame. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — aligned weight.",
