  "Creamed Spinach|Añejo Tequila": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness. Aged agave's warmth mirrors the side's richness. Strong — aligned depth.",
