  "Creamed Spinach|Basil Hayden's": "Creamed Spinach: dairy richness meets Basil Hayden's rye spice. Cleaner and brighter than wheated caramel takes here.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Basil Hayden's 10 Year": "Creamed Spinach: dairy richness meets aged rye spice. The 10-year adds oak depth to Basil Hayden's brighter-than-wheated profile.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Basil Hayden's Malted Rye": "Creamed Spinach: dairy richness meets bready malted grain. Bread-and-dairy logic built-in; malted rye threads through the cream in a way no other Basil Hayden's reaches.",
