  "Creamed Spinach|Bold / Premium Rye": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this bold rye's peppery spice and high-proof bite. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Bone Marrow": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. Shared-opener territory — starter and supporting plate run alongside each other. Strong — cohesive opener.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Bone-In Filet": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Strong — balanced plate.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Bourbon-Cask Speyside": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this Speyside Scotch's sherry cask, honeyed fruit, and elegant frame. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Bowdie's Old Fashioned": "Buffalo Trace muddled with our rum-soaked cherries, orange, and Angostura over a large cube. The bourbon's caramel depth meets the roux's parmesan and escargot-butter richness; works alongside a steak main with this side.",
