  "Creamed Spinach|Bowmore 12": "Creamed Spinach: dairy-rich side meets Bowmore 12's sherry depth. The honey threads into the cream; the gentler peat doesn't flatten the side the way Lagavulin or Laphroaig do. Works cleanly but won't move a guest.",
