  "Creamed Spinach|Canadian Whisky": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this Canadian whisky's smooth, light grain profile. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — aligned weight.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon": "Caymus — cocoa, mocha, velvety tannins. Heavier Napa Cab that matches the creamed spinach's weight; the tannin holds up against the parmesan-and-garlic roux. Peak pour when the table's ordering creamed spinach alongside a bigger cut.",
