  "Creamed Spinach|Evening Land Seven Springs": "Eola-Amity Hills Pinot — black cherry, smoked meat, dried rose, crushed stone. The smoked-meat note hooks into the escargot butter's garlic-shallot depth; serious Willamette Pinot that handles the roux's weight without backing down from it.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Exotic-Cask Finished Bourbon": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Extra Añejo Tequila": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness. Aged agave's warmth mirrors the side's richness. Strong — aligned depth.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon": "Oakville Napa Cab — blackcurrant, dark chocolate, espresso, violet, smooth powerful. The lush fruit and long finish ride our creamed spinach's weight perfectly; peak Cab pour when the table's going all-in.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Far Niente Chardonnay": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this rich, oak-aged Chardonnay's butter, stone fruit, and full-bodied weight. Opulent Chardonnay's butter and oak mirror the side's dairy richness — same-register match. Works — a capable side pour.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Fattoria Le Pupille Saffredi": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Faust Napa Valley Cabernet": "Agustin Huneeus's elegant Napa Cab — moderate tannin, fruit-forward, polished finish. Handles the creamed spinach well, but the bigger Cabs (Caymus, Far Niente) peak higher against the roux's weight and parmesan depth. Acceptable mid-tier Cab pour.",
  "Creamed Spinach|Filet Mignon": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Strong — balanced plate.",
