  "Creamed Spinach|Irish Whiskey": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this Irish whiskey's triple-distilled smoothness and light grain character. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
