  "El Cabo|Kansas City": "El Cabo with the KC — craft small-batch reposado, agave-forward character. Boutique production gives the pour distinctive craft voice; distinct from the big-brand reposados (Don Julio, Maker's etc.) by production scale alone. A craft-tequila strip call.",
