  "Elijah Craig Single Barrel|Truffle Fries": "Elijah Craig Single Barrel with truffle fries — 94-proof single-barrel against truffle-parmesan. The concentrated oak-spice gives the side grip at the premium Heaven Hill single-barrel register.",
