  "Elijah Craig Small Batch|Brussels and Belly": "Elijah Craig Small Batch with Brussels + Belly — spicy-sweet against maple-glazed pork belly. The small-batch oak cuts the glaze's sweetness cleanly; a grown-up bourbon for the small plate.",
  "Elijah Craig Small Batch|Burrata": "Elijah Craig Small Batch with burrata — fresh dairy against small-batch. Avoid.",
