  "Extra Añejo Tequila|Mocha Creme": "Extra Añejo Tequila: this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness meets this dense chocolate dessert's deep cocoa richness. Añejo's caramel and oak align with rich dessert sweetness. Works cleanly.",
  "Extra Añejo Tequila|Mushrooms": "Extra Añejo Tequila: this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness meets this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth. Aged agave's warmth mirrors the side's richness. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Extra Añejo Tequila|Peanut Butter Brownie": "Extra Añejo Tequila: this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness meets this dense chocolate dessert's deep cocoa richness. Añejo's caramel and oak align with rich dessert sweetness. Works cleanly.",
