  "Graham's 20 Year Tawny|Chocolate Brownie": "20-year oak-cask oxidative Tawny — Graham's step-up, concentrated dried fruit, roasted hazelnut, orange peel, silky long finish. The concentrated dried fruit wraps around fudge-brownie cocoa and the roasted hazelnut plays with whipped-chocolate frosting. Peak step-up Tawny for chocolate brownie — complexity handles the cocoa intensity.",
