  "Graham's 20 Year Tawny|Mocha Creme": "20-year oak-cask oxidative Tawny — Graham's step-up, concentrated dried fruit, roasted hazelnut, orange peel, silky long finish. The roasted hazelnut echoes espresso-roast directly and the orange peel lifts yolk-cream custard. Strong step-up Tawny for mocha creme — Vintage Port's intensity edges higher on espresso.",
