  "Grilled Caesar|Macauley Pinot Noir": "Grilled Caesar: the Grilled Caesar's charred romaine, anchovy umami, and bold creamy dressing meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. Cherry-driven red with the Caesar's umami and char — a classic cross-category salad pair. Strong — aligned register.",
