  "J Davies Ferrington Vineyards|Bone Marrow": "Anderson Valley Pinot against pure collagen-fat marrow — concentrated Mendocino Pinot still lacks the tannin needed to cut the render. Never pair. Route marrow to Cabs, Bordeaux, Meritage, or structured bold reds; keep J Davies Ferrington for the filet, chicken, or seafood course.",
