  "J. Davies Cabernet Sauvignon|Au Gratin Potatoes": "Diamond Mountain Cab — dark fruit, graphite, mineral backbone, firm tannin. The structured body cuts au gratin's cheese-and-cream weight and the graphite plays against the golden crust. Strong mountain Cab for au gratin — volcanic-soil complexity on the decadent side.",
  "J. Davies Cabernet Sauvignon|Bone Marrow": "Diamond Mountain Cab — volcanic dark fruit, graphite, mineral, firm tannin. The structured body meets marrow's rendered-fat richness and the graphite-mineral frames the bone depth. Strong mountain Cab for marrow — Schramsberg estate complexity and firm structure handle the rich starter.",
  "J. Davies Cabernet Sauvignon|Brussels and Belly": "J. Davies — Diamond Mountain Cab with dark fruit, graphite, mineral, firm tannin. The structured body handles pork-belly fat and the graphite plays against charred brussels. Strong mountain Cab for Brussels and Belly — volcanic complexity cuts the rich starter with Schramsberg provenance depth.",
