  "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak|Porterhouse": "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak with the porterhouse — double-barrel finish handles both strip and filet sides cleanly. The Twin Oak depth covers the plate in a way standard Jefferson's Reserve can't.",
  "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak|Seared Scallops": "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak with seared scallops — scallop delicacy against double-barrel oak. Avoid.",
  "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak|Shrimp Bisque": "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak with shrimp bisque — cream-based seafood against double-barrel. Works; the VR Twin Oak is over-specified for the soup's register.",
  "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak|Shrimp Cocktail": "Jefferson's Reserve VR Twin Oak with shrimp cocktail — cold shrimp against double-barrel. Avoid.",
