  "Jefferson's Reserve|Chocolate Brownie": "Jefferson's Reserve with the chocolate brownie — blended elegance against cocoa. Works; for cocoa interplay, Weller 107 or Weller Millennium bring more interplay with chocolate.",
  "Jefferson's Reserve|Cowboy Ribeye": "Jefferson's Reserve with the Cowboy Ribeye — 90-proof blended against cap fat and char. Strong; Jefferson's elegance is slightly underserved by the ribeye's scale — Jefferson's VR Twin Oak or Weller 12 handle this cut more fully.",
