  "Jefferson's Reserve|Filet Mignon": "Jefferson's Reserve with the filet — the blended elegance of Jefferson's signature profile. 90-proof honey, vanilla, and smooth oak frame the filet without aggressive character. Distinct from the Wellers' wheated softness or Buffalo Trace's straight oak — blending gives it a polished middle-ground. A refined everyday-premium call for filet.",
