  "Laurent Perrier Le Cuvée Brut|Aged Super-Premium Bourbon": "Laurent Perrier Le Cuvée Brut: this versatile sparkling's bright acidity, toasty lees character, and cleansing bubbles, considered as a bridge into this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
