  "Laurent Perrier Le Cuvée Brut|Asparagus": "Laurent Perrier Le Cuvée Brut: this versatile sparkling's bright acidity, toasty lees character, and cleansing bubbles meets this light, green vegetable's clean herbal edge. Sparkling acidity mirrors the vegetable's herbal brightness. Works cleanly.",
