  "London Dry Gin|Escargot": "London Dry Gin: this London Dry gin's juniper-forward, citrus-herbal frame meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. The spirit functions as a palate-setter here rather than a true counterpart to the plate. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
