  "Mijenta Blanco|Crab Cake": "Mijenta Blanco with crab cake — premium craft brand, Jalisco highlands, additive-free. Maestra Tequilera Ana Maria Romero's craft blanco; distinct from the big brands by additive-free philosophy and female-led production story. The clean craft agave lifts the crab with sustainability-focused craft character.",
