  "Milagro Reposado|Bone Marrow": "Milagro Reposado with bone marrow — triple-distilled reposado against umami fat. Strong; modern cleanness is capable but the starter earns a more character-forward reposado.",
  "Milagro Reposado|Brussels and Belly": "Milagro Reposado with Brussels + Belly — modern reposado against maple-glazed pork belly. Works; clean agave cuts the glaze but isn't a standout.",
  "Milagro Reposado|Cowboy Ribeye": "Milagro Reposado with the Cowboy Ribeye — modern 80-proof reposado against cap fat. Strong; the clean character is underpowered for the cut's scale — G4 High Proof is the high-impact reposado.",
  "Milagro Reposado|Crab Cake": "Milagro Reposado with crab cake — modern-style reposado against lump crab. The triple-distillation cleanness lifts the crab with modern simplicity; a clean contemporary reposado-seafood pairing.",
