  "Milagro Reposado|House Wedge": "Milagro Reposado with the House Wedge — modern reposado against iceberg and bleu. The clean agave character cuts the bleu with contemporary simplicity.",
  "Milagro Reposado|Kansas City": "Milagro Reposado with the KC — modern-style triple-distilled reposado. Clean agave with vanilla; distinct from traditional reposados (Siete Leguas) by production approach — Milagro is the modern clean pour. A contemporary everyday strip call.",
  "Milagro Reposado|Laurent Perrier Le Cuvée Brut": "Milagro Reposado into Laurent Perrier — triple-distilled reposado against sparkling. Cross-beverage miss.",
