  "Opus One|Clam Chowder": "Opus One: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight meets this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base. Bold red meets rich, caramelized depth — the wine's dark fruit threads through the savory base. Not a clean fit — the soup's register clashes.",
