  "Opus One|Head Fake": "Opus One: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight, considered as a bridge into this vodka cocktail's clean citrus lift and approachable sweetness. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
