  "Scotto Cellars The Lost Chapters|Truffle Fries": "California Cab by-the-glass — black cherry, cassis, dark chocolate, integrated medium tannin. The medium tannin cuts truffle-fry potato fat and the dark chocolate plays against the truffle-oil umami. Strong by-the-glass Cab for truffle fries — accessible California value on the umami hit.",
