  "Seafood Tower|London Dry Gin": "Seafood Tower: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this London Dry gin's juniper-forward, citrus-herbal frame. Clean spirit against a delicate starter — aperitif-register more than pairing. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
