  "Seared Scallops|Paloma": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this bright tequila cocktail's citrus lift and agave backbone. Light cocktail and delicate starter share the same register — fresh opener. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
