  "Seared Scallops|Porterhouse": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this bold, beefy strip's firm texture and savory char. Starter-into-steak flow — the opener sets up the main without stealing from it. Avoid — the starter overshadows or clashes with the main.",
