  "Seared Scallops|Veuve Clicquot Brut": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this versatile sparkling's bright acidity, toasty lees character, and cleansing bubbles. Sparkling's bubbles and acid scrub the starter's fat while the bright frame lifts the plate. A headliner starter pour.",
  "Seared Scallops|Vieux Carré": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Bold whiskey's weight meets the starter — register depends on the plate's richness. Avoid — too heavy for delicate starters.",
  "Seared Scallops|Weller 107": "Seared Scallops: scallop sweetness buried by bigger-body wheated. Avoid.",
  "Seared Scallops|Weller 12 Year": "Seared Scallops: clean caramelized scallop meets Weller 12 Year's aged wheated oak. Seafood can't carry the pour's weight; avoid.",
