  "Shrimp Bisque|Elk Cove Five Mountain": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. Strong — bright fruit lifts the weight.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Elk Cove Pinot Blanc": "Oregon Pinot Blanc — clean pear and apple fruit against the bisque's cream base. Doesn't peak the way a Chardonnay does, but always works. Reliable mid-tier white when the table splits pours.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Espresso Old Fashioned": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this coffee-driven cocktail's bitter roast, rich texture, and dessert-adjacent sweetness. Coffee cocktail against a savory plate — wrong register entirely. Works only as a transition pour.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Evening Land Seven Springs": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. A confident warmth match.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Exotic-Cask Finished Bourbon": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Cocktail against a creamy seafood soup — acidity and lift cut the dairy base while the spirit carries its own weight. Avoid.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Bold red meets rich, caramelized depth — the wine's dark fruit threads through the savory base. Works when the soup's weight supports the tannin.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Far Niente Chardonnay": "Napa Chardonnay — oak, tropical fruit, rounder body. California Chard loves cream bisque; the oak matches the 2-3 hour shell-stock depth and the tropical fruit plays against the coconut milk sweetness. Peak white pour.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Fento Ollo de Sapo Mencía": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. Works — coherent if not a headliner.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Filet Mignon": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Strong — balanced plate.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Fisher Unity Pinot Noir": "Sonoma Pinot — riper and rounder than the Willamette Avni. Works if the guest is Pinot-committed; the fruit-forward profile meets the coconut milk sweetness without fighting the shellfish stock base or the smoked paprika finish.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Four Roses Yellow Label": "Shrimp Bisque: cream-based seafood meets entry bourbon. Works neutrally; light body sits with the soup.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|French 75": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this gin cocktail's citrus brightness and botanical lift. Cocktail against a creamy seafood soup — acidity and lift cut the dairy base while the spirit carries its own weight. Works cleanly.",
