  "Shrimp Bisque|Herbal / Anise Liqueur": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this amaro's bitter-herbal complexity and Italian digestif depth. Amaro + bitter intersects with creamy + seafood — the pairing lands on weight and flavor alignment. A strong match — the register aligns cleanly.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Highland Scotch": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this Highland Scotch's honey, heather, and light-fruit character on a medium body. Smoother whiskey against a creamy seafood soup — oak and vanilla mesh with the dairy base. Works cleanly.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Irish Whiskey": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this Irish whiskey's triple-distilled smoothness and light grain character. Smoother whiskey against a creamy seafood soup — oak and vanilla mesh with the dairy base. Strong — aligned depth.",
