  "Shrimp Bisque|Japanese Whisky": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this Japanese whisky's delicate fruit, floral lift, and elegant restraint. Smoother whiskey against a creamy seafood soup — oak and vanilla mesh with the dairy base. Strong — aligned depth.",
