  "Shrimp Bisque|Jean-Pierre Grossot Chablis": "Burgundy Chablis, mineral acid, oyster-shell character. Cuts through the heavy cream and coconut milk base, handles the smoked paprika finish. The precision pick when the richness of the bisque needs a counterpoint.",
