  "Shrimp Cocktail|Opus One": "Mondavi-Rothschild's $950 prestige Cabernet — completely overpowering for a cold-shellfish starter. The wine buries the shrimp and the sauces. Never pour here; steer Opus toward the steak course where it performs.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Paloma": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this bright tequila cocktail's citrus lift and agave backbone. Light cocktail and delicate starter share the same register — fresh opener. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
