  "Shrimp Cocktail|Paul Bara Grand Rosé Brut": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this sparkling rosé's strawberry-and-brioche charm with crisp acidity. Sparkling's bubbles and acid scrub the starter's fat while the bright frame lifts the plate. Strong — palate-cleansing start.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Peju Cabernet Sauvignon": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. Elegant red's cherry and silk mirror the starter's register — light-on-light or bright-on-rich depending on the plate. Avoid.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Pierre Gimonnet Special Club Brut": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this versatile sparkling's bright acidity, toasty lees character, and cleansing bubbles. Sparkling's bubbles and acid scrub the starter's fat while the bright frame lifts the plate. Strong — palate-cleansing start.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Pineau des Charentes": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets the Pineau's grape-sweet, cognac-warmed aperitif profile. Dessert-register fortified meets savory food — the sweetness usually overruns the dish. A headliner when the savory plate has sweet depth (glazed, caramelized, umami-rich).",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Pio Cesare Barbaresco": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
