  "Shrimp Cocktail|Sherried Speyside": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this Speyside Scotch's sherry cask, honeyed fruit, and elegant frame. The whiskey sits heavy against a starter; the match depends on whether the plate has fat to scrub. Avoid — too heavy for delicate starters.",
