  "Shrimp Cocktail|The Happy Wife": "Tito's with orange juice and ginger syrup, stirred with a brûléed orange garnish. The OJ's sweetness balances the cocktail sauce's horseradish heat; the ginger adds warmth. Approachable pour for a guest who wants something easy.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|The Prisoner Red Blend": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Transfusion": "Hangar 1 vodka muddled with black grapes and lime, topped with ginger beer. The grape fruit and ginger-beer effervescence keep the drink light enough for cold shrimp. More complex than it looks; honest fit.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Trombo Cedano Reposado": "Shrimp Cocktail: cold shrimp meets cedar-aged reposado. Strong; cedar character novel but competes with cocktail sauce.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Venge Family Reserve": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Venge Scout's Honor": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Venge Silencieux": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Vesper": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this dry, spirit-forward gin cocktail's bitter-herbal complexity. Both lean bright and clean — no weight fighting weight, just an easy start to the meal. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Veuve Clicquot Brut": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this versatile sparkling's bright acidity, toasty lees character, and cleansing bubbles. Sparkling's bubbles and acid scrub the starter's fat while the bright frame lifts the plate. A headliner starter pour.",
