  "Shrimp Cocktail|White / Light Rum": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this white rum's clean sugarcane, tropical lift, and light frame. Clean spirit against a delicate starter — aperitif-register more than pairing. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
