  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Bowdie's Old Fashioned": "Siete Leguas Blanco into Bowdie's Old Fashioned — tahona-crushed against house cocktail. Cross-beverage miss.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Burrata": "Siete Leguas Blanco with burrata — rustic traditional blanco against fresh mozzarella. The craft character gives the burrata more texture than polished blancos provide.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon": "Siete Leguas Blanco into Caymus — traditional blanco against Napa Cab. Cross-beverage miss.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Crab Cake": "Siete Leguas Blanco with crab cake — traditional tahona-crushed blanco, family-distillery craft. Rustic, earthier agave than Don Julio's polished benchmark; the traditional character gives the crab more texture than globally-marketed blancos bring.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Escargot": "Siete Leguas Blanco with escargot — traditional blanco against garlic-butter snails. Strong; the rustic craft cuts the garlic-butter with distinctive texture.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Faroe Island Salmon": "Siete Leguas Blanco with the salmon — traditional craft against salmon's richness. Strong; the rustic character is distinctive but less refined a salmon match than Don Fulano Blanco or Don Julio Blanco.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Filet Mignon": "Siete Leguas Blanco with the filet — traditional craft blanco against the 8oz cut. Works; blanco isn't the natural filet call.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Grilled Caesar": "Siete Leguas Blanco with the grilled Caesar — tahona-crushed against charred romaine. Strong; earthy agave matches the Caesar's weight.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|House Wedge": "Siete Leguas Blanco with the House Wedge — tahona-crushed traditional against iceberg and bleu. The earthier agave cuts the bleu with craft distinctiveness.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Market Fish": "Siete Leguas Blanco with the market fish — traditional craft against catch of the day. Works; rustic blanco lifts the fish depending on preparation.",
  "Siete Leguas Blanco|Opus One": "Siete Leguas Blanco into Opus One — rustic craft against marquee Cab. Cross-beverage miss.",
