  "Spiced / Flavored Rum|Carrot Cake": "Spiced / Flavored Rum: this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth meets the carrot cake's warm-spice, cream-cheese indulgence. Aged rum or cognac with rich dessert — classic after-dinner move. A headliner dessert spirit.",
  "Spiced / Flavored Rum|Cheesecake": "Spiced / Flavored Rum: this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth meets the cheesecake's dense, tangy dairy richness. Aged rum or cognac with rich dessert — classic after-dinner move. A headliner dessert spirit.",
