  "Spiced / Flavored Rum|Scavino Barolo": "Spiced / Flavored Rum: this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth, considered as a bridge into this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
